2.title: Auditions #2
2.plot: In the search to find the best amateur home cook in America, only a few more hopefuls have the opportunity to present their signature dish to judges Gordon Ramsay, Joe Bastianich and Graham Elliot. Some chefs wow the judging panel with their raw talent and many fall flat, but one thing is for certain: all of the home cooks endure an intense grilling. The remaining contestants pour their hearts into their creations in order to convince the judges they have the potential to take the culinary world by storm.

1.title: Auditions #1
1.plot: In Part One of the two-night season premiere, award-winning chef Gordon Ramsay, restaurateur Joe Bastianich and acclaimed chef Graham Elliot return to the MasterChef judging panel. After a nationwide search, only the best amateur cooks - including a stock broker, a professional opera singer, a plastic surgeon, as well as the first blind cook to enter the competition - were flown to Los Angeles for a chance to prepare their signature dishes and present them to the judges. The judges will taste for flavor, originality, creativity and presentation. But most importantly, ...

2.title: Auditions #2
2.plot: In Part Two of the two-night Season Premiere, the auditions continue as the judges critique the good and the bad and continue to winnow down the competition. Those who impress the judges will earn a coveted white apron and move one step closer to becoming the next MasterChef.

imdb.plot outline: MasterChef is a television cooking game show franchise created by Franc Roddam, which originated with the UK version of the show in 1990. The same MasterChef logo is used around the world and has become well known in many countries over the years.
imdb.title: MasterChef Romania
plot: A nationwide search for the best home cooks in Romania. One of 50 hopefuls will become a culinary star and one of Romania's Masterchefs.::Cosmin Agafitei
